                mapping: [{"browser":[0,0],"sizes":[[320,250],[300,250]]},{"browser":[898,1],"sizes":[[970,1],[950,250],[600,155],[728,210],[728,180],[728,90],[720,300],[970,90],[970,300],[970,250],[970,480],[400,400],[600,425],[640,480],[928,120]]}],
                viewports: ["desktop","mobile"]
            };

                            var isEnabled = true;
            
            if (isEnabled && typeof FF.adSlotManager !== 'undefined' && typeof FF.AdSlot !== 'undefined')
            {
                FF.adSlotManager.register(new FF.AdSlot(slotData));
            }
            else if (isEnabled)
            {
                window.moneySlots.push(slotData);
            }
        }
        else
        {
            document.querySelector('.footer__branding').remove();
        }
    </script> </div> </div> <div class="footer__bottom"> <div class="footer__left"> <div class="footer__logo-social"> <a href="https://www.forexfactory.com" data-touchable="" title="Homepage"></a> <ul
